From: "David Hildenbrand (Arm)" <david@kernel.org>
Date: Fri, 27 Feb 2026 21:08:38 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] mm/memory: rename unmap_single_vma() to __zap_vma_range()

Let's rename it to better fit our new naming scheme.

